                                .font(.subheadline)
                                .frame(maxWidth: .infinity)
                                .padding(.vertical, 8)
                        }
                        .liquidGlassCard(isInteractive: true, tintColor: .blue)
                    }
                }

                // Best practices
                VStack(alignment: .leading, spacing: 8) {
                    Text("💡 Best Practices")
                        .font(.headline)

                    VStack(alignment: .leading, spacing: 4) {
                        bulletPoint("Use AnimatedGlassContainer to group morphing cards")
                        bulletPoint("Assign unique .glassID() to each morphing element")
                        bulletPoint("Use @Namespace property wrapper")
                        bulletPoint("Combine with .spring() animation for best results")
                        bulletPoint("Spacing parameter (40.0) controls morph distance threshold")
